subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text: Combination of kwukyel script {{l|ko|丷|tr=ha|pos=top part of {{l|ko|為|tr=wi|pos=hun-reading: {{ko-l|하다|to do, to be}}}}}} and radical {{l|ko|ㄗ}} or simplified form of {{l|ko|阝|pos=left part of {{l|ko|隱|tr=eun}}}} which indicates final consonant ''-n''.
